WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
♪I found a faint light
in the fading dusk♪

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
♪And met your steady gaze♪

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
♪One knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on♪

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
♪We made a promise long ago♪

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
♪For all our days to come♪

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
♪How much must I let go
to trade for one moment?♪

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
♪Holding you close♪

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.874
♪Would that be enough?♪

00:00:58.875 --> 00:00:59.499
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:01.599
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:03.499
=Episode 8=

00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:05.519
(Shengtang Guild:
trafficking money, trading leverage)

00:01:05.519 --> 00:01:07.432
(records of Beauty Portrait,
colluding for profit)

00:01:07.580 --> 00:01:09.598
The Shengtang Guild operates
under a strict hierarchy.

00:01:09.598 --> 00:01:11.099
Officials from every faction at court

00:01:11.099 --> 00:01:12.800
are bound together
through exchanges of power and desire,

00:01:12.800 --> 00:01:15.360
forming cliques for private gain,
and expanding their circle of allies.

00:01:15.360 --> 00:01:16.780
The rules here are numerous.

00:01:17.059 --> 00:01:18.700
Each member fulfills a specific role,

00:01:18.900 --> 00:01:20.500
and they work together seamlessly.

00:01:22.259 --> 00:01:23.140
Brothel Keeper

00:01:24.139 --> 00:01:26.459
controls the major pleasure quarters
in the Capital,

00:01:26.460 --> 00:01:28.258
and selects performers
for the Shengtang Guild.

00:01:28.259 --> 00:01:29.099
Auction Master

00:01:31.259 --> 00:01:33.058
oversees auctions
and selects performers,

00:01:33.059 --> 00:01:34.860
then distributes the spoils
to various officials.

00:01:34.979 --> 00:01:35.579
Enforcer

00:01:35.580 --> 00:01:36.899
silences witnesses through killing,

00:01:36.900 --> 00:01:38.720
and eliminates political rivals
for the Shengtang Guild.

00:01:38.720 --> 00:01:39.720
Chief Steward

00:01:39.979 --> 00:01:41.819
is responsible
for handling the cleanup.

00:01:43.460 --> 00:01:45.060
A bunch of beasts.

00:01:45.312 --> 00:01:47.157
(Shengtang Guild: Brothel Keeper,
Enforcer, Auction Master, Chief Steward)

00:01:48.380 --> 00:01:50.179
We must take matters into our hands.

00:01:50.580 --> 00:01:51.858
They may soon find out

00:01:51.859 --> 00:01:53.107
that I took Su Wanniang's place.

00:01:53.139 --> 00:01:54.860
They will surely come after us.

00:01:56.499 --> 00:01:57.299
Instead,

00:01:58.139 --> 00:01:59.659
(Shengtang Guild)
we should strike first.

00:02:01.740 --> 00:02:03.739
Have we not already obtained
the Beauty Portrait?

00:02:03.740 --> 00:02:05.700
It must contain evidence
of their crimes.

00:02:05.979 --> 00:02:08.658
There is no time to lose. We will deliver it
to the Court of Judicial Review now,

00:02:08.659 --> 00:02:10.220
and bring them all to justice.

00:02:12.700 --> 00:02:14.899
Although the Beauty Portrait
is crucial evidence,

00:02:14.900 --> 00:02:16.699
the proof is still not sufficient.

00:02:16.700 --> 00:02:18.259
We need a witness.

00:02:18.980 --> 00:02:21.580
Only then will we stand
a full chance of victory.

00:02:24.580 --> 00:02:27.900
The Beauty Portrait has been sent
to the Imperial Guard for investigation.

00:02:28.099 --> 00:02:29.460
A witness?

00:02:32.020 --> 00:02:34.098
You should not have come here today.

00:02:34.099 --> 00:02:36.900
Speak. What exactly is your purpose?

00:02:37.140 --> 00:02:38.900
I do not understand what you mean.

00:02:39.140 --> 00:02:40.378
Have you not suffered enough

00:02:40.379 --> 00:02:41.618
up to this point?

00:02:41.619 --> 00:02:43.739
The Shengtang Guild is
different from Huanyue House.

00:02:43.740 --> 00:02:46.179
In the past, you may have survived

00:02:46.180 --> 00:02:47.419
with a few petty tricks.

00:02:47.499 --> 00:02:49.778
But once you step through
the gates of the Shengtang Guild,

00:02:49.779 --> 00:02:51.460
there's no turning back.

00:02:51.980 --> 00:02:53.580
You will have no tomorrow.

00:02:54.300 --> 00:02:54.979
Oh, right.

00:02:54.980 --> 00:02:56.780
I remember the man who bought me that day.

00:02:56.939 --> 00:02:58.538
His behavior was very strange.

00:02:58.539 --> 00:03:00.378
He had the chance to make a move against me,

00:03:00.379 --> 00:03:01.900
yet he did nothing.

00:03:02.140 --> 00:03:04.658
And his voice sounded very familiar.

00:03:04.659 --> 00:03:06.740
He also knew I was not Su Wanniang.

00:03:07.099 --> 00:03:09.900
That means he is likely someone
from the pleasure house.

00:03:12.379 --> 00:03:13.179
It seems

00:03:13.180 --> 00:03:14.900
we must return to Huanyue House.

00:03:17.140 --> 00:03:18.099
Wei Cheng.

00:03:20.420 --> 00:03:21.539
Sir.

00:03:23.140 --> 00:03:24.300
Miss Song.

00:03:24.700 --> 00:03:25.778
Your mission

00:03:25.779 --> 00:03:27.139
has now been completed.

00:03:27.140 --> 00:03:28.299
I informed you

00:03:28.300 --> 00:03:30.020
because what follows will be dangerous.

00:03:30.180 --> 00:03:31.819
Once this matter is concluded,

00:03:31.939 --> 00:03:35.139
I will retrieve your indenture contract
from Huanyue House and return it to you.

00:03:35.339 --> 00:03:36.058
For the time being,

00:03:36.059 --> 00:03:37.218
remain at the Gu Residence

00:03:37.219 --> 00:03:38.379
and focus on recovering.

00:03:43.659 --> 00:03:44.780
Gu Chengye.

00:03:46.580 --> 00:03:47.659
Gu Chengye.

00:03:48.379 --> 00:03:49.179
At this point,

00:03:49.180 --> 00:03:50.780
how do you expect me
to walk away unscathed?

00:03:52.339 --> 00:03:53.659
You scoundrel!

00:03:58.260 --> 00:03:59.658
This fox-masked man

00:03:59.659 --> 00:04:01.740
was willing to spend a fortune to save her.

00:04:03.260 --> 00:04:05.099
There must be more to it.

00:04:07.180 --> 00:04:09.299
Perhaps he is the witness
we are looking for.

00:04:09.300 --> 00:04:10.299
I will go at once.

00:04:10.300 --> 00:04:11.300
Wait.

00:04:14.539 --> 00:04:15.739
Give Miss Song

00:04:15.740 --> 00:04:17.380
a chance to leave.

00:04:17.979 --> 00:04:19.099
Then follow her.

00:04:20.979 --> 00:04:22.699
So, you mean

00:04:22.700 --> 00:04:24.460
to let Miss Song go instead?

00:04:25.380 --> 00:04:26.979
What a calculated move.

00:04:33.099 --> 00:04:34.020
Remember,

00:04:34.779 --> 00:04:36.299
assign more covert guards.

00:04:36.580 --> 00:04:38.260
You must ensure her safety.

00:04:39.940 --> 00:04:41.059
Yes, sir.

00:04:59.979 --> 00:05:02.900
You dared to let Song Zhiyun escape.

00:05:03.140 --> 00:05:05.419
Do you have any idea
how much trouble you have caused?

00:05:05.739 --> 00:05:07.338
Those above have already learned

00:05:07.339 --> 00:05:10.380
that Song Zhiyun entered the Guild
impersonating Su Wanniang.

00:05:12.219 --> 00:05:13.780
I failed my duty.

00:05:14.659 --> 00:05:16.099
Failed your duty?

00:05:16.380 --> 00:05:18.059
You did it on purpose.

00:05:18.339 --> 00:05:20.820
If they find out it was you,

00:05:21.140 --> 00:05:23.179
we will all die.

00:05:23.380 --> 00:05:24.858
At the mass graves east of the city,

00:05:24.859 --> 00:05:27.059
there is already a spot
reserved for you.

00:05:29.140 --> 00:05:30.499
I was wrong.

00:05:30.539 --> 00:05:31.859
From now on,

00:05:32.419 --> 00:05:34.700
I will obey your order, Master Zhou.

00:05:50.580 --> 00:05:51.700
Come.

00:05:59.739 --> 00:06:00.979
Well, well.

00:06:01.140 --> 00:06:03.380
If you had been a little more obedient
these past years,

00:06:03.539 --> 00:06:06.580
you would not have suffered
such torment.

00:06:18.020 --> 00:06:19.260
(Gu Chengye,)

00:06:19.299 --> 00:06:20.940
(do you really think
you can lock me up?)

00:06:21.339 --> 00:06:23.707
(Shangguan Yu is very likely that fox.)

00:06:23.739 --> 00:06:25.299
(And he will not harm me.)

00:06:25.662 --> 00:06:27.700
(Once I persuade him to be the witness,)

00:06:27.739 --> 00:06:29.460
(you're not going to
look down on me later.)

00:06:30.700 --> 00:06:32.924
Well now, sir,

00:06:32.925 --> 00:06:35.178
why are you here all alone?

00:06:35.179 --> 00:06:36.858
The ladies here

00:06:36.859 --> 00:06:39.059
are all skilled in music,
chess, calligraphy, and painting.

00:06:39.060 --> 00:06:41.900
We guarantee your visit
will not be in vain.

00:06:44.460 --> 00:06:45.979
This way, honored guest.

00:06:56.179 --> 00:06:58.459
(What a handsome young gentleman.)

00:06:58.460 --> 00:07:00.499
(He looks either wealthy or noble.)

00:07:00.700 --> 00:07:02.298
(If I could win his heart,)

00:07:02.299 --> 00:07:04.099
(I might free myself
from this lowly status.)

00:07:06.500 --> 00:07:07.978
You're sitting here alone.

00:07:07.979 --> 00:07:09.640
Is it that a kindred spirit
is hard to find?

00:07:09.640 --> 00:07:10.459
Perhaps

00:07:10.460 --> 00:07:12.780
I could keep you company.

00:07:13.260 --> 00:07:14.418
(Darn it.)

00:07:14.419 --> 00:07:16.460
(Why did she have to show up
at a time like this?)

00:07:16.580 --> 00:07:18.020
(She must not ruin my plan.)

00:07:18.099 --> 00:07:20.939
There is no need to trouble your, miss.
Things have been tense lately.

00:07:20.940 --> 00:07:22.859
Keep an eye out for suspicious people.

00:07:26.179 --> 00:07:28.059
Since a kindred spirit is hard to find,

00:07:28.900 --> 00:07:30.099
why not

00:07:30.900 --> 00:07:32.539
share a drink with me?

00:07:43.460 --> 00:07:46.259
It is all Song Zhiyun's fault
that I missed my chance to perform

00:07:46.260 --> 00:07:48.045
and was demoted
to a low ranked performer.

00:07:48.299 --> 00:07:49.499
Otherwise,

00:07:49.500 --> 00:07:51.739
I would already be a concubine
in a great household by now.

00:07:52.580 --> 00:07:54.979
That wretched woman
had better never return.

00:07:56.580 --> 00:07:58.974
Was it Shangguan Yu

00:07:58.975 --> 00:08:00.580
who demoted you?

00:08:00.779 --> 00:08:01.920
Chief Yu?

00:08:03.200 --> 00:08:04.321
No.

00:08:04.859 --> 00:08:07.619
He has always looked after me in secret.

00:08:07.940 --> 00:08:08.739
Then

00:08:09.099 --> 00:08:10.700
where is he now?

00:08:11.900 --> 00:08:13.979
Chief Yu...

00:08:14.179 --> 00:08:16.311
He was just punished by Master Zhou.

00:08:16.312 --> 00:08:17.659
He is

00:08:19.299 --> 00:08:20.499
upstairs.

00:08:25.099 --> 00:08:26.220
Su Wanniang.

00:08:27.060 --> 00:08:28.179
Su Wanniang.

00:08:49.340 --> 00:08:50.940
Who are you?

00:08:52.299 --> 00:08:54.139
You are actually a woman.

00:08:54.740 --> 00:08:56.180
You are a woman too.

00:08:57.140 --> 00:08:58.820
Who exactly are you?

00:09:21.337 --> 00:09:23.257
It's you.